00:24:38,749 --> 00:24:41,279
Kamu bisa beristirahat keesokan harinya.

481
00:24:45,590 --> 00:24:47,519
Apartemennya bergerak.

482
00:24:50,559 --> 00:24:51,959
Semua lampu ini.

483
00:24:52,029 --> 00:24:53,160
Banyak sekali.

484
00:24:53,229 --> 00:24:55,130
